descript.abstract: This is the County of San Diego, Department of Parks and Recreation polygon Parks_CN layer, representing County Park-specific owned, co-owned, leased, funded or cooperatively managed park units. Because this dataset includes managed, leased or co-owned properties, overlap with other property owners or management agencies will be apparent if using similar property-based layers.Attributes and CodingLabel: ShapeDefinition: Feature geometryLabel: OBJECTIDDefinition: System generated keyLabel: carto_nameDefinition: Park unit name. overview.eaover: This is the County of San Diego, Department of Parks and Recreation polygon Parks_CN layer, representing County Park-specific owned, co-owned, leased, funded or cooperatively managed park units. Attribute item NAME_FULL is the full name of the park unit. Attribute item CARTO_NAME is the is the abbreviated park name (often a first park of the name), to reduce overlapping type conflicts in cartographic products, by ommission of a portion of the name or by displaying/stacking two lines of type in conjuntion witth abbribute item CARTONAME2, or when DPR requests not to use a portion of the full name. Attribute item CARTONAME2 is a second part of a full park name (NAME_Full) and is used with CARTO_NAME in type stacking to reduce type conflicts in cartographic products. Attribute item PARK_TYPE contains a categorical listing of park types.
